description:
P9AirMax mobile phone wireless over-ear bluetooth headset heavy bass 
 Bluetooth wireless headset over-ear subwoofer headset with microphone for Xiaomi/Huawei/iPhone 
 Transmission range: 15 meters Functions: power display, call function, voice control, support music, multi-point connection, wearing sensor Bluetooth protocol: 5.0 Channel: Stereo How to use: Head-mounted Single and double ears: bilateral stereo Color: Space gray, silver, sky blue, green, pink Chip type: Jerry Battery life: 12 (hours) 
 Features: wearing sensor, connection use, Chinese and English prompts, voice assistant, etc 
 Automatically detect the wearing status of the headset, and when the headset is removed, the audio automatically pauses; 
 The dome mesh on the headband is made of tight, breathable fabric that helps to disperse weight and reduce pressure on the head; 
 The inside of the ear tips adopts a concave structure, which greatly increases the activity space of the ears and is more comfortable when wearing; 
 The telescopic sleeve adopts a one-piece molding process, which is beautiful and stable in the position you want, and always fits snugly when worn; 
 Retractable earmuffs, 110° rotating earmuffs, easy to carry around; 
 Using self-developed utility model patent technology, the Type-c interface of the headset can realize the functions of charging and audio connection, and the built- 
 in microphone of the headset can still support calls and button operations after connection; 
 400mAh polymer battery, built-in protection chip, up to 12 hours of listening life; 
 Charging for 10 minutes can play continuously for about 2.5 hours, solving emergency charging needs; 
